{"tid":975447,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"置地旗下公司入稟高院　追討海航829萬欠款","createTime":"2019-01-09T15:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T15:44:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd2da10dcda3adcc08bba0ae23eb740a13d11cfa","tid":975447,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190109/s00001/eeb74ce301b7f4f34f13a5c96470a7fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2Feeb74ce301b7f4f34f13a5c96470a7fe.jpg&h=b3226a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海航集團（國際）有限公司遭香港置地旗下公司Mulberry Land Company Limited，入稟高院追討829萬欠款。<br />\n<br />\n該公司指，海航原定須於去年12月1日及今年1月1日就一份契約支付929萬，惟海航只支付了100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n海航回應時表示，公司前期由於受流動性困難影響，造成遲付，相關款項現已全部付清。"},{"pid":"f2c9953c57178d65acb5aecf34ad081b79a80334","tid":975447,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e41f5cc5c55a95a2ca9214a71e14438129b76f","tid":975447,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1547021403588&amp;issue=20190109\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1547021403588%26issue%3D20190109&d=4%2BvgcLjDEU85daVKvUDpCv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=637e51d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1547021403588&amp;issue=20190109</a><br />\n<br />\n【海航賣產】傳海航以近33億元出售曼哈頓大樓<br />\n<br />\n根據《彭博》報道，海航出售曼哈頓第三大道850號大樓，以圖降低公司財政負擔。報道提到，由於該大樓鄰近美國總統特朗普的特朗普大廈，是次交易有助緩和美國政府對國家安全的憂慮，以及為中美緊張的關係降溫。<br />\n<br />\n該集團在一份聲明中提到，海航已完成上述交易，但沒有提供細節，有指買家為當地發展商Chetrit集團創辦人Jacob Chetrit及其兒子，售價4.22億美元（折合約32.9億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n據報，海航於2016年斥資逾4.63億美元（折合約36.1億港元）購入該大廈九成業權，並於去年起於市場放售。假如該廈以上述成交價易手，意味海航帳面已錄得虧損。"}]}